content: TEST: [2025, Age 22] Just got back from Japan, and the way they integrate technology into daily life has me rethinking everything. Had a chat with Hiroshi, a local dev, about how AI could revolutionize our blockchain projects. Time to bring some of that innovation back to NYC!
